name: ai9000
description: Delaunch.ai is a decentralized platform that enables the co-creation and co-ownership of AI agents with an emphasis on transparency, collaboration, and scalability. These AI agents, powered by cutting-edge machine learning models and secured by blockchain technology, excel in diverse fields such as gaming, virtual environments, customer interaction, and creative ventures. Rooted in the ethos of Web3, Delaunch.ai ensures fair distribution of ownership, governance, and benefits among its participants.
